 ██████▀████  ████  ████▄████▀██▄█████▀ ██████▀
   Smacs - short macs editor

BASICS:
Notations C means <Ctrl>
		  M means <Meta> or <Alt>
		  Ido means Emacs features.
		  (Interactively DO thing with buffers and files)

----------------------------------------------------------------------
CURSOR MOVEMENT:
Backward character ......... C-b	Forward character ............ C-f
Previous line .............. C-p	Next line .................... C-n
Previous word .............. M-b	Next word .................... M-f
Beggining of line .......... C-a	End of line .................. C-e
Scroll up .................. C-v	Scroll down .................. M-v
Beggining of buffer......... M-<	End of buffer ................ M->
----------------------------------------------------------------------
FILE COMMAND:
Find file .................. C-o
Save file .................. C-c
----------------------------------------------------------------------
EDITING COMMAND:
Delete next character....... C-d	Delete prev. character <Backspace>
Move line up ............... M-n	Move line down ............... M-n
Paste ...................... C-y    Duplicate line ............... C-,
Kill line .................. C-k
----------------------------------------------------------------------
REGION/SELECTION:
Set mark ................... C-SPC  Set mark forward ............. M-@
Exit selection ............. C-g
Cut ........................ C-w    Copy ......................... M-w
Replace .................... C-y    Wrap region in parenthesis ... M-(
Delete region ...... <Backspace>	Delete region ................ C-d
Upper case region .......... M-u	Lower case region ............ M-l
----------------------------------------------------------------------
SEARCH:
Search forward ............. C-s	Search backward .............. C-r
Next search match ...... <Enter>    Exit searching ............... C-g
----------------------------------------------------------------------
VIEW:
Font size decrease ......... C--	Font size increase ........... C-=
Toggle full window ......... F11	Recenter top bottom .......... C-l
Split pane ...... C-x sp <Enter>	Next pane .................... C-q
Close pane ................. M-k

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
MISCELLANEOUS:
Switch buffer .............. C-i	Go to line ....... C-x :{N} <Enter>
Ido next match ............. C-s	Go to next line .. C-x n{N} <Enter>
Ido previous match ......... C-r	Go to prev. line . C-x p{N} <Enter>
									Absolute number .. C-x dlabs<Enter>
									Relative number .. C-x dlrel<Enter>
									Disable number ... C-x dlnon<Enter>
